                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Solliciteren",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>We gaan vandaag aandacht besteden aan solliciteren.</p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "image",
                            "src": "https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/5/58b9617b2f8370331d60dca4f733edec8a381d99.jpg",
